touch on the stalled Cyprus peace talks in his meeting with
Turkish officials since Britain is one of the major international
mediators for the issue.
</P>
<P>
Turkish-EU relationship has been tense since the EU rejected
Turkey's membership efforts and accused the Muslim country of poor
human rights record, poor economic performance as well as creating
tensions with Greece. 
