also made a decision to finalize elimination of tariff obstacles and
expediting trade activities in the meeting of the ECO delegations
to be held in Tehran. However, he did not mention when the meeting
would be held in Iran.
</P>
<P>
The Iranian president, who arrived in Almaty on Sunday, also
said that campaign against narcotics and contraband goods which
would damage the economic relations of the 10 ECO member states
were among other achievements of the summit.
</P>
<P>
Referring to his talks with the heads of other member
countries, he said that he discussed the legal regime of the
Caspian Sea with some of the heads of the littoral states.
</P>
<P>
The ECO was founded in 1985 by Iran, Turkey and Pakistan. Six
former Soviet republics and Afghanistan joined it in 1992. 
</P>
