Ilves expressed his satisfaction for the Estonia-China
ties. "Although Estonia is a small country and China is a big one,
the two share some common points," he said.
</P>
<P>
He said both China and Estonia have hard-working peoples and
hope to develop mutually friendly ties.
</P>
<P>
The two foreign ministers also exchanged views on international
issues of common concern.  
