The full impact of the Lahore High Court order against Hub
Power Company LTD was felt by the Karachi Stock Exchange in the
morning session Tuesday when foreign and institutional buyers
indulged in heavy selling in energy stocks. At the close of the
morning session, the KSE-100 Index was down by 53.24 points.
