very weak," said Davar Hasan, a trader from UBS Securities in
Karachi.
</P>
<P>
Traders predict further falls in the week. "I expect more falls
as foreign investor confidence has been shattered over the IPP's
(Independent Power Producers') issue," said Aqeel Karim Dhedi, one
of the largest traders at the Karachi bourse. 
