PARIS -- United Nations Secretary-General Kofi Annan will meet
here on Tuesday with Iraqi Vice Prime Minister Tarik Aziz,
U.N. officials said in Paris.
</P>
<P>
Annan, who is on a three-day visit here, will make a statement
after the meeting.
</P>
<P>
This will be the first meeting between Annan and Aziz when the
U.N. secretary-general signed an agreement on the U.N. inspection
of Iraqi presidential sites with Aziz in Baghdad on February
23. (France-UN-Iraq) 
</P>
