fast in the '90s, with the trade volume rising by 300%, he
noted. During his stay here, he met with Chinese leaders and
discussed with them issues of bilateral relations so as to create
favourable environment for the further development of bilateral
cooperation, he said.
</P>
<P>
He told reporters that Swedish Chamber of Commerce in China
with 50 member companies was set up on Sunday.
