fund for which the Federation of Malaysian Consumer Associations
has offered to be the coordinator.
</P>
<P>
More than 200 local and foreign companies are taking part in
the four-day exhibition.
</P>
<P>
Malaysia suffered seriously from a haze resulting from forest
fires in neighboring Indonesia last year and is facing the
problems of open burning in the country. 
